features: FOOD-GRADE SILICONE COOKING UTENSILS SET: The silicone utensils set is made entirely of odorless food-grade silicone, which is BPA-free and has good scratch resistance to protect the non-stick coating on the cookware and extend its service life.

HIGH TEMPERATURE RESISTANCE: These silicone kitchen utensils sets can withstand temperatures up to 446°F (230°C). You can use them in boiling water or hot oil. The all-around silicone adds softness, so no more worrying about food sticking to your cookware or creating odors. This allows chefs to use them to easily stir and flip food without you having to worry about scratching the surface of your non-stick cookware.

LARGE KITCHEN UTENSILS SET: Each piece of cutlery is upgraded to a large size and offers a perfectly balanced weight and elegant design. The high quality wooden handles provide a comfortable grip and ensure complete prevention of heat transfer. Each piece is specifically designed to take your cooking to a higher level.

EASY TO CLEAN: With silicone cooking utensils, cleaning is a breeze. Simply hand wash with warm water and soap and you're ready to clean in seconds. Do not soak. Not suitable for dishwasher cleaning. In addition, silicone is abrasion resistant and durable, maintaining its premium appearance and performance even with frequent use.

GREAT VALUE SET: Each piece of cutlery offers a perfectly balanced weight and elegant design that will enhance your kitchen decor.The 6-piece set includes everything from soup spoons, solid spoons, slotted turners, solid turners, pasta servers and spatulas. The exquisite packaging and reasonable price make it the perfect gift for your mother or friend.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Large Silicone Cooking Utensils Set Looking for durable, heat-resistant cooking utensils? Hvygss' kitchen utensils are made of scratch-free, pliable silicone material that can withstand temperatures from -22°F/-30°C to 230°C/446F. These 6 cooking utensils fulfill basic cooking needs and are a must-have for your new house or apartment kitchen. Each piece of cookware has its own unique purpose and they will be a great addition to your kitchen.
You can hang them in the corners of your kitchen through the small holes at the top of the wooden handles to decorate your kitchen and keep them organized.

High temperature resistance (230°C/446F) The soft silicone spatula head protects your pans from scratching or denting the surface. These cookware won't chip, warp or melt like old plastic cookware. Silicone cookware can withstand high temperatures up to 446°F/230°C.

Food-grade silicone wrapped nylon, the two become one without any seams. Enhanced durability and toughness prevents spatulas from bending or warping for all heavy-duty flipping needs. This silicone cooking utensil will not react with food or beverages.

Create mouth-watering meals with our professional kitchen utensils. Designed with super-polished wooden handles that are both easy to hold and easy to manage, these cookware utensils will help you create delicious meals!
